dataObject.name: Survey for finding a fitting day

Description
This process reflects the planning of a LAN party with several friends. Two different forms are used to request the required information from the friends and transfer it into the own planning process.
- There must be at least 8 friends at one date - It must be clarified which games are played - A suitable tag for the LAN party must be found - The beer demand must be clarified
